reviews.review_text:
MBT-A! Mason B. Taylor...Awesome!
I've yet to listen to a Mason B. Taylor AUD pull that I didn't like... and this one is top-notch, too!  The Scarlet-/>Fire is teriffic - especially the nice, extended Scarlet jam - and the Drums just thunders!  The Wheel out of Space is played nice & slow, the 'Round & 'Round-/>JBG to close has the entire joint jumpin', and the UJB encore is the perfect capper!
